# Welcome to Accelerant Software Github Pages
These pages are exclusively for documentation using some of Accelerant's open source tools.

## Projects

### Axelstrap
Axel strap is a custom front-end framework designed for legacy applications. This framework attempts to leverage modern front-end patterns and syntax. 

### Essbase Aliazer
Essbase Aliazer is an open source project that provides additional alias based search tools for Essbase.
